7.40	Anthony_Adverse	Anthony Adverse	Anthony Adverse is a 1936 American drama film directed by Mervyn LeRoy. The screenplay by Sheridan Gibney is based on the sprawling 1,224-page novel of the same title by Hervey Allen.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/9f/AnthonyAdverse.jpg/220px-AnthonyAdverse.jpg
